transcript:
Customer: Hello

Executive: Haan, maine link kab pe click kiya hai, join kijiye aap.

Executive: Mam, konsi company se baat kar rahe hain?

Executive: Hello

Executive: Haan ji haan ji mam boliye join kar rahe hain aap, ek baar join kariye.
Customer: Join ki.
Executive: Neel Meg se baat kar rahe hain na mam aap?
Customer: Neel Meg nahi hai toh woh.
Executive: Neel Meg se baat kar rahe hain, konsi company se?
Customer: Meenu Commercial se baat kar rahe hain.
Executive: Meenu Commercial se na, aap ek baar join kariye, kariye mam.

Customer: Ek second.
Executive: Usi same link pe rahega mam.
Customer: Haan haan main aa.
